  <title>Change cursor</title>

  <p>There are 3 cursors available in <app>Terminal</app></p>
  
  <list type="numbered">
    <item>
      <p>⎜ called <gui>I-Beam</gui>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>▐ called <gui>Block</gui>.</p>
    </item>
    <item><p> _  called <gui>Underline</gui>.</p>
    </item>
  </list>

  <p>Go to <guiseq><gui style="menu">Edit</gui><gui style="menuitem">Profile Preferences</gui><gui style="tab">General</gui></guiseq> and choose desired cursor from the menu next to <gui>Cursor shape</gui>.</p>

